OL,3,CFamily-owned golf club put up for sale
OL,4,Cwith #10 million price tag
OL,6,FJersey's Les Mielles Golf and Country
OL,7,FClub has been listed for sale for
OL,8,F#9.95m.
OL,10,FThe 62-acre site in St Ouen, including
OL,11,Ftwo nine-hole courses, a clubhouse,
OL,12,Fshop, restaurant, bar and beauty
OL,13,Fsalon, has been in the same family for
OL,14,Ffour generations.
OL,16,FThe facility also has admin offices,
OL,17,Fstaff accommodation and a 125-space
OL,18,Fcar park.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
