FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781878274
OL,3,CFamily-owned golf club put up for sale
OL,4,Cwith #10 million price tag
OL,6,FDirector of golf and co-owner Jonathan
OL,7,FLe Brun says it was "not an easy
OL,8,Fdecision" but they "believe now is the
OL,9,Fright time to hand over the reins".
OL,11,FThe site will continue to operate as
OL,12,Fnormal, including current memberships
OL,13,Fand subscriptions, the club has
OL,14,Fconfirmed.
OL,16,FLes Mielles sits within Jersey's
OL,17,FNational Park and has been running
OL,18,Fsince the 1960s, when it was converted
OL,19,Ffrom a family farm.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
