OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781878274
OL,3,CFamily-owned golf club put up for sale
OL,4,Cwith #10 million price tag
OL,6,FThe family say they are not selling
OL,7,Fbecause the club is struggling, they
OL,8,Fjust felt it was time for a change.
OL,10,FMr Le Brun adds: "The business is
OL,11,Frunning efficiently, generating income
OL,12,Ffrom several complementary streams.
OL,14,F"Everything is in place for a smooth
OL,15,Ftransition. We see real potential for
OL,16,FLes Mielles to evolve into a modern
OL,17,Fclub where golf meets lifestyle."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
