OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781878274
OL,3,CFamily-owned golf club put up for sale
OL,4,Cwith #10 million price tag
OL,6,FProperty agent Geri O'Brien from
OL,7,FSavills Jersey says: "The scale of the
OL,8,Flandholding in such a special setting
OL,9,F- combined with its established
OL,10,Fbusiness and infrastructure - offers a
OL,11,Fcompelling platform for future
OL,12,Fownership and investment.
OL,14,F"It's a rare turnkey opportunity with
OL,15,Fscope for further enhancement."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
